            Ideal for bulk list cleaning or high-value sign-up flows.
          </p>
          <span class="tag tag-service">💼 Enterprise / High Volume</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="alt-item">
        <div class="alt-number">6</div>
        <div class="alt-content">
          <h4>Layered Approach (Recommended in Practice)</h4>
          <p>
            Combine: <strong>1)</strong> lightweight regex for instant UX feedback →
            <strong>2)</strong> MX lookup on form submit →
            <strong>3)</strong> confirmation email for account activation.
            Each layer catches different failure modes without over-blocking valid addresses.
          </p>
          <span class="tag tag-best">🏆 Best Practice</span>
