| Service | What It Checks |
|---|---|
| **ZeroBounce** | Syntax + DNS + SMTP mailbox ping |
| **NeverBounce** | Deliverability score + catch-all detection |
| **Abstract API** | MX, SMTP, disposable email detection |
| **Mailgun Validation** | Full validation + did-you-mean suggestions |

