---

## The Honest Summary

| Approach | Catches Typos | RFC Compliant | Proves Deliverability |
|---|---|---|---|
| Regex | Mostly | ❌ No | ❌ No |
| HTML5 `type="email"` | Mostly | ❌ No | ❌ No |
| RFC library | Yes | ✅ Yes | ❌ No |
| MX DNS lookup | Yes | ✅ Yes | Partially |
| Confirmation email | Yes | ✅ Yes | ✅ **Yes** |

**Regex is a UX courtesy, not validation.** The only ground truth is whether the user can click a link you sent them.

